2026-01-16 15:17:12,637 - INFO - Line : # Linking EventRecord to OperationPlan via pep:ProcedureExecutionContainer
2026-01-16 15:17:12,637 - INFO - Line : # This is an example of how an EventRecord might be part of a procedure execution container,
2026-01-16 15:17:12,637 - INFO - Line : # which itself might be related to an OperationPlan.
2026-01-16 15:17:12,637 - INFO - Line : # For simplicity, I'll link the TroubleTicketNote to a hypothetical procedure execution container.
2026-01-16 15:17:12,637 - INFO - Line : # The schema states: "a TroubleTicketNote is a context for (potentially) many *CorrectiveMaintenanceAction* to occur; hence it relates to a `pep:ProcedureExecutionContainer`"
